  "experiment_info": {
    "experiment_count": 1,
    "experiments": [
      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "在连续滴流床反应器中，使用双功能Pt-Beta 25-粘合剂催化剂，在30 bar氢气压力、40 mL/min气体流速和0.5 mL/min液体流速（异丁子香酚/十二烷混合物，0.012 M）条件下，对异丁子香酚进行加氢脱氧反应，以生产可再生喷气燃料范围内的丙基环己烷。催化剂筛选在150°C下进行，以确定金属位置、催化剂酸度和铂颗粒尺寸的影响。还使用在沸石和粘合剂上均负载铂的催化剂，在65至200°C的温度范围内研究了温度对活性和催化剂失活的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Hydrodeoxygenation of isoeugenol in a continuous trickle-bed reactor to produce propylcyclohexane... All catalytic tests were performed at 30 bar of hydrogen, with a gas flow rate of 40 mL min−1, and a liquid flowrate of 0.5 mL min−1 of a mixture of isoeugenol in dodecane (0.012M). Screening of the catalysts was performed at 150°C... The effect of temperature on activity and catalyst deactivation was determined using the catalyst with platinum supported on both the zeolite and the binder. A range of temperatures between 65 and 200°C was used...",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
